 812, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"QMS chief sales officer, Tim Murphy, said the partnership with the Australian Olympic Committee has supercharged the outdoor player's ability to showcase the benefits of being a digital-first out of home network during the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 1086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\", \"score\": 0.6987114528906249, \"rank\": 0.4312059146796484, \"text\": \"QMS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Murphy_(American_politician)\", \"score\": 0.5478073799118423, \"rank\": 0.6587901701323685, \"text\": \"Tim Murphy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Murphy_(American_politician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Murphy_(American_politician)\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the partnership\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the outdoor player's ability\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefits\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"home network\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For example, our breaking news headlines were delivered so quickly that we were live across our billboards nationally with the Australian Women's 4 x 100m Relay team gold medal to